The Protectors of Kronos SMO was formed in 1997 by seven citizens of Elodis.

The founding members were:  Henk Bodrogi, Carmine Osvaldo, Ale L. Hanne, Jeroen Karel, Valentine Mies, Yanick Cato and Joreto Katell.
